": \"the flag\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3203}, {\"ngram\": \"her home country\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zerouala also pointed to the importance of Kaylia Nemour, one of France's top gymnasts, who chose to switch nationalities and compete for Algeria after a protracteddisputewith the French gymnastics federation, which was inflexible about where the 17-year-old gymnast trained.\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3291, \"end\": 3297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8496623484340249, \"rank\": 0.1769381020189023, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3364, \"end\": 3371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999999936344466, \"rank\": 6.365373769726863e-09, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 3406, \"end\": 3434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French gymnastics federation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Gymnastics_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Gymnastics_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zerouala\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3234}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3265}, {\"ngram\": \"Kaylia Nemour\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3282}, {\"ngram\": \"nationalities\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3347}, {\"ngram\": \"a protracteddisputewith\", \"from\": 3378, \"to\": 3401}, {\"ngram\": \"the 17-year-old gymnast\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zerouala dubbed Nemour's gold-medal win on the uneven bars \\\"a colonial reparation.\\\"\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \