r sex\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3823}, {\"ngram\": \"gender\", \"from\": 3828, \"to\": 3834}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3868, \"to\": 3872}, {\"ngram\": \"Franceas\", \"from\": 3876, \"to\": 3884}, {\"ngram\": \"an Algerian\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 3896}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif's refusal\", \"from\": 3897, \"to\": 3913}, {\"ngram\": \"French\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 3929}, {\"ngram\": \"her last press conference\", \"from\": 3933, \"to\": 3958}, {\"ngram\": \"Arabic\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 3977}, {\"ngram\": \"English\", \"from\": 3982, \"to\": 3989}, {\"ngram\": \"a politics\", \"from\": 4008, \"to\": 4018}, {\"ngram\": \"resistance\", \"from\": 4022, \"to\": 4032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Politicians often try to exploit the Olympics-and Olympic athletes-for their political careers.\", \"from\": 4079, \"to\": 4174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Politicians\", \"from\": 4079, \"to\": 4090}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics-and Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4145}, {\"ngram\": \"their political careers\", \"from\": 4150, \"to\": 4173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this backfired for French President Emmanuel Macron, whose constant, unrequested hugging of any French Olympian within his five-meter radius was off-putting.\", \"from\": 4175, \"to\": 4336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4198, \"end\": 4214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 4215, \"end\": 4230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emmanuel Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 4275, \"end\": 4281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9829917226872886, \"rank\": 0.011442742948012025, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4282, \"end\": 4290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.198512800494501e-16, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whose constant, unrequested hugging\", \"from\": 4232, \"to\": 4267}, {\"ngram\": \"his five-meter radius\", \"from\": 4298, \"to\": 4319}, {\"ngram\": \"off-putting\", \"from\": 4324, \"to\": 4335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After French judoka Romane Dicko won bronze, Macron cupped her head in his hands, an experience that, she said, made her feel \\\"a little embarrassed.\\\"\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4343, \"end\": 4349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9829917226872886, \"rank\": 0.011442742948012025, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4382, \"end\": 4388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.978261874105083e-38, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 4374, \"to\": 4380}, {\"ngram\": \"her head\", \"from\": 4396, \"to\": 4404}, {\"ngram\": \"his hands\", \"from\": 4408, \"to\": 4417}, {\"ngram\": \"an experience\", \"from\": 4419, \"to\": 4432}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French Olympian Hugo Hay, who qualified for the final in the 5000 meters, even called out Macron for his brazen politicking,declaring, \\\"These are not his Games, but those of the athletes.\\\"\", \"from\": 4487, \"to\": 4675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4487, \"end\": 4493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9829917226872886, \"rank\": 0.011442742948012025, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4577, \"end\": 4583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.978261874105083e-38, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 5000 meters\", \"from\": 4544, \"to\": 4559}, {\"ngram\": \"his brazen politicking\", \"from\": 4588, \"to\": 4610}, {\"ngram\": \"his Games\", \"from\": 4637, \"to\": 4646}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Macron's tanned visage also evinced a cacophony of jeers when it appeared on the jumbotron at the Olympic fan zone in Place de la Bataille Stalingrad during the gold-medal men's basketball game between the United States and France.\", \"from\": 4677, \"to\": 4908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4677, \"end\": 4683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.978261874105083e-38, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}, {\"begin\": 4883, \"end\": 4896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.5995581548213766, \"rank\": 0.6678949188811621, \