ain unresolved.\", \"from\": 5102, \"to\": 5202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5178, \"end\": 5183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.881787752853673e-26, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the media hullabaloo\", \"from\": 5107, \"to\": 5127}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 5133, \"to\": 5151}, {\"ngram\": \"serious social issues\", \"from\": 5153, \"to\": 5174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To police the Olympics, there were heavily armed security forces from more than 30 different countries, but that is not all.\", \"from\": 5203, \"to\": 5327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5213, \"to\": 5225}, {\"ngram\": \"heavily armed security forces\", \"from\": 5238, \"to\": 5267}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 30 different countries\", \"from\": 5273, \"to\": 5305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France's political leaders also transformed the city into their ownpanopticon, with the French National Assembly greenlighting the use of algorithmic video surveillance.\", \"from\": 5328, \"to\": 5497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5328, \"end\": 5334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8496623484340249, \"rank\": 0.1769381020189023, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5416, \"end\": 5440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Parliament\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4546926449606446e-56, \"text\": \"French National Assembly\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Parliament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Parliament\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 5372, \"to\": 5380}, {\"ngram\": \"their 