 when charges were dropped, to justify arresting him a second time, he said.\", \"from\": 6679, \"to\": 6802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Police officers\", \"from\": 6679, \"to\": 6694}, {\"ngram\": \"his previous arrest\", \"from\": 6706, \"to\": 6725}, {\"ngram\": \"charges\", \"from\": 6732, \"to\": 6739}, {\"ngram\": \"a second time\", \"from\": 6779, \"to\": 6792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The experience, he told us, \\\"worries me for what's to come\\\" after the Games.\", \"from\": 6803, \"to\": 6879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The experience\", \"from\": 6803, \"to\": 6817}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 6827, \"to\": 6829}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 6869, \"to\": 6878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Off the field, the most under-discussed story were the people in Paris who paid for the Olympics with their shelter and sense of stability.\", \"from\": 6881, \"to\": 7020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6946, \"end\": 6951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.881787752853673e-26, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 6885, \"to\": 6894}, {\"ngram\": \"the most under-discussed story\", \"from\": 6896, \"to\": 6926}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 6932, \"to\": 6942}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 6965, \"to\": 6977}, {\"ngram\": \"their shelter\", \"from\": 6983, \"to\": 6996}, {\"ngram\": \"sense\", \"from\": 7001, \"to\": 7006}, {\"ngram\": \"stability\", \"from\": 7010, \"to\": 7019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About12,500 unhousedand precariously housed people were bused out of the city.\", \"from\": 7021, \"to\": 7099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"About12,500 unhousedand\", \"from\": 7021, \"to\": 7044}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 7065, \"to\": 7071}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 7090, \"to\": 7098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Making the city \\\"Olympics ready\\\" meant a \\\"social cleansing\\\"-or what activists fromLe Revers de la M\\u00e9daille(The Other Side of the Medal) callednettoyage social.\", \"from\": 7100, \"to\": 7259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 7107, \"to\": 7115}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Olympics\", \"from\": 7116, \"to\": 7125}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"social cleansing\\\"-or\", \"from\": 7139, \"to\": 7162}, {\"ngram\": \"what activists\", \"from\": 7163, \"to\": 7177}, {\"ngram\": \"M\\u00e9daille(The Other Side\", \"from\": 7198, \"to\": 7221}, {\"ngram\": \"the Medal\", \"from\": 7225, \"to\": 7234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some were given shelter; others, their whereabouts are unknown.\", \"from\": 7260, \"to\": 7323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"shelter\", \"from\": 7276, \"to\": 7283}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 7285, \"to\": 7291}, {\"ngram\": \"their whereabouts\", \"from\": 7293, \"to\": 7310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was an Olympic-size human rights travesty that deserved more coverage.\", \"from\": 7324, \"to\": 7399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic-size human rights travesty\", \"from\": 7333, \"to\": 7370}, {\"ngram\": \"more coverage\", \"from\": 7385, \"to\": 7398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, attention shifts to Los Angeles, host of the 2028 Summer Games.\", \"from\": 7401, \"to\": 7469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7426, \"end\": 7437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1053982608768021e-31, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Now, attention shifts\", \"from\": 7401, \"to\": 7422}, {\"ngram\": \"host\", \"from\": 7439, \"to\": 7443}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2028 Summer Games\", \"from\": 7447, \"to\": 7468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The finale of the Paris 2024 closing ceremony involved a gaudy, star-studded handoff of the torch to LA Mayor Karen Bass.\", \"from\": 7470, \"to\": 7591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7488, \"end\": 7498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8070402024700522e-35, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 7580, \"end\": 7590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karen Bass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The finale\", \"from\": 7470, \"to\": 7480}, {\"ngram\": \"a gaudy, star-studded handoff\", \"from\": 7525, \"to\": 7554}, {\"ngram\": \"the torch\", \"from\": 7558, \"to\": 7567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But not even the shine from Snoop Dogg's golden shoes could blind Kenneth Mejia, LA's city controller, from the grim realities that differentiate LA from Paris.\", \"from\": 7592, \"to\": 7752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7620, \"end\": 7630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 7658, \"end\": 7671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenneth_Mejia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenneth Mejia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenneth_Mejia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenneth_Mejia\"}, {\"begin\": 7746, \"end\": 7751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank