l enrichment to the tune of billions of dollars during an affordability crisis, a foreign policy guided only by his own derelict sense of morality, and the deployment of a murderous campaign of occupation, detention, and deportation on American streets.\", \"from\": 8766, \"to\": 9158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8807, \"end\": 8819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999899956, \"rank\": 9.868589045411234e-12, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 9141, \"end\": 9149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.087742833661092e-18, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 8778, \"to\": 8786}, {\"ngram\": \"the reasons\", \"from\": 8791, \"to\": 8802}, {\"ngram\": \"untrammeled corruption\", \"from\": 8871, \"to\": 8893}, {\"ngram\": \"personal enrichment\", \"from\": 8898, \"to\": 8917}, {\"ngram\": \"the tune\", \"from\": 8921, \"to\": 8929}, {\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 8933, \"to\": 8941}, {\"ngram\": \"dollars\", \"from\": 8945, \"to\": 8952}, {\"ngram\": \"an affordability crisis\", \"from\": 8960, \"to\": 8983}, {\"ngram\": \"a foreign policy\", \"from\": 8985, \"to\": 9001}, {\"ngram\": \"his own derelict sense\", \"from\": 9017, \"to\": 9039}, {\"ngram\": \"morality\", \"from\": 9043, \"to\": 9051}, {\"ngram\": \"the deployment\", \"from\": 9057, \"to\": 9071}, {\"ngram\": \"a murderous campaign\", \"from\": 9075, \"to\": 9095}, {\"ngram\": \"occupation\", \"from\": 9099, \"to\": 9109}, {\"ngram\": \"detention\", \"from\": 9111, \"to\": 9120}, {\"ngram\": \"deportation\", \"from\": 9126, \"to\": 9137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now an undeclared, unauthorized, unpopular, and unconstitutional war of aggression against Iran has spread like wildfire through the region and into Europe.\", \"from\": 9160, \"to\": 9316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9251, \"end\": 9255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"score\": 0.9999999977180778, \"rank\": 2.281855062772764e-09, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an undeclared, unauthorized, unpopular, and unconstitutional war\", \"from\": 9164, \"to\": 9228}, {\"ngram\": \"aggression\", \"from\": 9232, \"to\": 9242}, {\"ngram\": \"wildfire\", \"from\": 9272, \"to\": 9280}, {\"ngram\": \"the region\", \"from\": 9289, \"to\": 9299}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 9309, \"to\": 9315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A new \\\"forever war\\\"-with an ever-increasing likelihood of American troops on the ground-may very well be upon us.\", \"from\": 9317, \"to\": 9430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9375, \"end\": 9383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.087742833661092e-18, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an ever-increasing likelihood\", \"from\": 9342, \"to\": 9371}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 9394, \"to\": 9404}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 9427, \"to\": 9429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As we have seen over and over, this administration uses lies, misdirection, and attempts to flood the zone to justify its abuses of power at home and abroad.\", \"from\": 9432, \"to\": 9589, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this administration\", \"from\": 9463, \"to\": 9482}, {\"ngram\": \"lies\", \"from\": 9488, \"to\": 9492}, {\"ngram\": \"misdirection\", \"from\": 9494, \"to\": 95